data.description: Nestled within the charming Rainbow Acres subdivision in Dunnellon, Florida, this remarkable 6-bedroom, 4.5-bath home is a true gem. Situated on a sprawling .92-acre lot, this two-story residence spans 2,876 square feet under air, providing ample space for all your needs and desires.    Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere in the foyer overlooking the formal living room.   As you ascend the stairs, you'll find the landing, hallway, and stairs adorned with brand-new luxury vinyl plank flooring, which adds a touch of elegance and durability to the space.      The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring stainless steel appliances that were recently replaced in 2022. The washer and dryer will also stay with the sale of the home, providing added convenience for the new owners. A walk-in pantry ensures that you have ample storage for all your culinary needs.    The property is equipped with a well and septic system, offering cost-effective and reliable utility services. High-speed internet is available, keeping you connected in today's digital world.    Updated LED lighting and fixtures throughout the home not only enhance energy efficiency but also create a bright and welcoming ambiance. For added peace of mind, a whole-house propane generator is in place, ensuring that you never experience disruptions in power supply.    A new slider with enclosed blinds leads to a patio area, perfect for outdoor entertaining and relaxation. A storage shed provides additional space for your tools and equipment, while the 3-car garage offers ample parking and storage options.    The master bedroom is located upstairs, offering privacy and tranquility, while a second master bedroom downstairs provides flexibility and convenience. Four of the bedrooms have direct access to full bathrooms, making mornings a breeze for everyone.  The 6th bedroom could also be used as a nursery or office.    This home is conveniently located close to Rainbow Springs, known for its natural beauty and outdoor recreational opportunities. Don't miss your chance to own this exquisite property in the heart of Dunnellon, Florida, where comfort, convenience, and luxury come together to create the perfect place to call home.
